<!--
  PriceGrab on-screen brandmark.

  A small price-tag silhouette tinted with the active ColorScheme's
  primary role, used inside the Compare screen's top app bar
  immediately before the plain-text "PriceGrab" title. The glyph
  echoes the launcher icon's price-tag intent without copying the
  launcher's photographic detail (which would not survive at 24dp).

  Geometry: 24x24 viewport so it slots cleanly into the Material 3
  default top-app-bar leading space without resizing. The single
  path below is the canonical Material "local offer" tag silhouette
  with a soft inner cut for the tag eyelet, kept simple so it
  remains crisp on every density bucket.

  Decorative: marked invisibleToUser at the call site
  (CompareScreen.kt) — TalkBack reads "PriceGrab" from the title
  text only, never twice.
-->
